At around 5:24AM Madison Police Officers responded to the 200 block of N. Marquette St for a report of shots fired. Officers located an occupied residence that had been struck by gun fire. No injuries have been reported and the investigation is ongoing.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
If you have any information regarding the incident, please contact MPD at 608-255-2345, or you can remain anonymous and contact Madison Area Crime Stoppers at 608-266-6014, or, on the web at p3tips.com.&nbsp;

