On Saturday, August 6, 2022 at approximately 5:10am, Madison Police were dispatched to a traffic crash involving a single motor vehicle and pedestrian.&nbsp; This crash occurred on westbound USH 12, near Agriculture Dr.&nbsp; Unfortunately the pedestrian involved in the crash succumbed to his injuries and was pronounced deceased at the scene.&nbsp; The driver of the motor vehicle is cooperating with the investigation.<br />
